{"tid":54712,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"入左U之後覺得好孤獨","createTime":"2016-12-25T18:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T12:02:41.000Z","uid":66772,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19ec76543e43ee95a9aa983be60ea171abedd5dd","tid":54712,"uid":66772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:33:53.000Z","msg":"上年DSE放榜成績唔理想，下定決心要閉關retake，都唔會話要出去玩，而本身熟果d fd可能都廢時阻我溫書從來唔約我。<br />\n一年黎身邊d fd去哂唔同地方讀書，各散東西。但係有樣野佢地係一樣，就係佢地仲係好fd成日約。眼見一個一個同我冇哂聯絡，我有試過約下佢地出黎。但出到黎唔知點解有種隔膜，好似好陌生。我好希望可以同佢地fd 返，但奈何佢地唔知係嫌我悶定係覺得我變左，已經唔再會搵我。<br />\n<br />\n後尾，好好彩我入得返u，諗住可以識到班新fd。開頭係玩得幾埋，可惜又發現佢地各自有自己既best fd，或者好fd既中同，永遠最重要既節日都係同佢地出面d fd過。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日放假，見中同個個一堆堆玩得好開心，大學fd又同中同玩得好開心。回望下自己，雖則叫做有d大學既朋友，但係都覺得好孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2db1482173e5f1c6620c1c02eb58009db778ee","tid":54712,"uid":66772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:34:36.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"686a65b8cfaa4685695735892e5dcb1a6f13ad74","tid":54712,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:34:58.000Z","msg":"有冇hall雞"},{"pid":"716faa96b21300efe2e8cdfc73e255b85f5db98d","tid":54712,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇hall雞</blockquote><br />\n有"},{"pid":"7a4a44d5a5d97faae2690f1ca93f79734833fef9","tid":54712,"uid":66772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"毒撚第一次開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有人回下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a945fb70128794e076f435f947b98fa396e2aec7","tid":54712,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"加油 會搵到屬於你既圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi